GET http://localhost:3002/booking/artisans
Authorization: Bearer 

###

# Get available service requests for artisan (requires ARTISAN role + APPROVED status)
GET http://localhost:3002/booking/requests/available
Authorization: Bearer 

###

# Artisan accepts a service request
POST http://localhost:3002/booking/request/1/accept
Authorization: Bearer <ARTISAN_BEARER_TOKEN>
